<subSubSection id="68AA6541B853FFA0FF330671CF73FD80" pageId="10" pageNumber="54" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="200F36CAB853FFA0FF330671CF73FD80" blockId="10.[151,1436,152,526]" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">
Note:— 
<taxonomicName id="E7B04D49B853FFA0FED10671CF0BFEC5" authorityName="Zarrei &amp; Wilkin" authorityYear="2011" baseAuthorityName="Zarrei &amp; Wilkin" baseAuthorityYear="2011" box="[292,598,306,332]" class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Gagea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="10" pageNumber="54" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="section" section="Tricholloydia">
<emphasis id="12C4EAD8B853FFA0FED10671CC2FFEC5" box="[292,370,306,331]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">Gagea</emphasis>
sect. 
<emphasis id="12C4EAD8B853FFA0FE4D0671CF0BFEC5" box="[440,598,306,331]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">Tricholloydia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
comprises members of 
<taxonomicName id="E7B04D49B853FFA0FC870671C9F2FEC5" box="[882,1199,306,332]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Phallaceae" genus="Lloydia" kingdom="Fungi" order="Phallales" pageId="10" pageNumber="54" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="section" section="Tricholloydia">
<emphasis id="12C4EAD8B853FFA0FC870671CE96FEC5" box="[882,971,306,331]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">Lloydia</emphasis>
sect. 
<emphasis id="12C4EAD8B853FFA0FBE40671C9F2FEC5" box="[1041,1199,306,331]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">Tricholloydia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
that are included in 
<taxonomicName id="E7B04D49B853FFA0FF62061ACDB8FEFC" authorityName="Salisb. However, Farr &amp; Zijlstra" authorityYear="1996" box="[151,229,345,370]" class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Gagea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="10" pageNumber="54" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="12C4EAD8B853FFA0FF62061ACDB8FEFC" box="[151,229,345,370]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">Gagea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a section for the first time here. 
<taxonomicName id="E7B04D49B853FFA0FD8A061ACE2DFEFC" authority="Rafinesque, 1837" authorityName="Rafinesque" authorityYear="1837" box="[639,880,345,370]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Hemierium" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="10" pageNumber="54" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="graecum">
<emphasis id="12C4EAD8B853FFA0FD8A061ACE2DFEFC" box="[639,880,345,370]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">Hemierium graecum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(L.) 
<bibRefCitation id="44214B3BB853FFA0FC5E061AC9EDFEFD" author="Rafinesque, C. S." box="[939,1200,345,371]" pageId="10" pageNumber="54" refId="ref10442" refString="Rafinesque, C. S. (1837) Flora Telluriana. Philadelphia: H. Probasco." type="book" year="1837">Rafinesque (1837: 27)</bibRefCitation>
was designated as a 
<typeStatus id="FF0B8868B853FFA0FF6206C3CC52FE14" box="[151,271,384,410]" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">lectotype</typeStatus>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="44214B3BB853FFA0FEB106C3CFD8FE14" author="Dasgupta, S. &amp; Deb, D. B." box="[324,645,384,410]" pageId="10" pageNumber="54" pagination="104 - 112" refId="ref8876" refString="Dasgupta, S. &amp; Deb, D. B. (1986) Taxonomic revision of the genus Lloydia (Liliaceae) in India and adjoining region. Indian Journal of Forestry 9: 104 - 112." type="journal article" year="1986">Dasgupta &amp; Deb (1986)</bibRefCitation>
. It is synonymous with 
<taxonomicName id="E7B04D49B853FFA0FC3006C3C919FE17" box="[965,1092,384,409]" class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Gagea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="10" pageNumber="54" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="graeca">
<emphasis id="12C4EAD8B853FFA0FC3006C3C919FE17" box="[965,1092,384,409]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">G. graeca</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<typeStatus id="FF0B8868B853FFA0FBAD06C3C98DFE14" box="[1112,1232,384,410]" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="E7B04D49B853FFA0FAF406C3CC67FE4E" class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Gagea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="10" pageNumber="54" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="section" section="Anthericoides">
<emphasis id="12C4EAD8B853FFA0FAF406C3C808FE17" box="[1281,1365,384,409]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">Gagea</emphasis>
sect. 
<emphasis id="12C4EAD8B853FFA0FF6206E4CC67FE4E" box="[151,314,423,448]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">Anthericoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Therefore, the typification of 
<bibRefCitation id="44214B3BB853FFA0FD5F06E5CE9AFE4E" author="Dasgupta, S. &amp; Deb, D. B." box="[682,967,422,448]" pageId="10" pageNumber="54" pagination="104 - 112" refId="ref8876" refString="Dasgupta, S. &amp; Deb, D. B. (1986) Taxonomic revision of the genus Lloydia (Liliaceae) in India and adjoining region. Indian Journal of Forestry 9: 104 - 112." type="journal article" year="1986">Dasgupta &amp; Deb (1986)</bibRefCitation>
is rejected here, and a new typification has been made. Other species of 
<taxonomicName id="E7B04D49B853FFA0FDEC068ECF2FFE68" box="[537,626,461,486]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Phallaceae" genus="Lloydia" kingdom="Fungi" order="Phallales" pageId="10" pageNumber="54" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="12C4EAD8B853FFA0FDEC068ECF2FFE68" box="[537,626,461,486]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">Lloydia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
need to be studied both morphologically and in terms of typification before transferring them to 
<taxonomicName id="E7B04D49B853FFA0FE2C06B7CF7AFD83" authorityName="Salisb. However, Farr &amp; Zijlstra" authorityYear="1996" box="[473,551,500,525]" class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Gagea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Liliales" pageId="10" pageNumber="54" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="12C4EAD8B853FFA0FE2C06B7CF7AFD83" box="[473,551,500,525]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="54">Gagea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
